16. LOOPS — while, do-while, for
 
 # while
@int i is 0$
loop (i lt 10) begin
    i is i + 1$
end
 # do while
@int i is 0$
repeat begin
    i is i - 1$
end loop (i gt 0)$
# for
@int i is 0$
iterate (i is 0 $ i lt 5$ i is i + 1) begin
    @int x is i * 2$
end


